Rize Mesh Node
====================

Rize Mesh Node was developed by:

Michele Riso
Giuseppe Zerbo

Rize Mesh Node is derived from Barnacle, developed by szym.net

Rize Mesh Node is a combination of tools to setup a Mesh Network 
on an Android phone:
 * NAT
 * DHCP server
 * WLAN ad-hoc setup

How to build Rize Mesh Node
---------------------

Prerequisites:                                                                                                                                                                                                       
1) Android NDK r4 or above                                                                                                                                                                                           
2) Eclipse and ADT plugin                                                                                                                                                                                            
                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
To build native components enter Rize Mesh Node root directory and run                                                                                                                                                     
$NDK/ndk-build                                                                                                                                                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
where NDK=path-to-your-ndk-directory                                                                                                                                                                                 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
To build the Android app import the existing project into Eclipse and export                                                                                                                                         
an .apk file.

